        <description>Thousands of years ago a trace of unusual darkness appeared in the sky, since then these black-hooded figure and the army under their command have ravaged around this rimworld, until some time ago they suddenly decide to shrink their influence back into their outposts and facilities.\n\nIt's widly believed the Whelingnorther Alliance origins from a far distant Midworld long time ago, when its first generation members were seeking a new ideology different from any present and then persued and hunted by the two super authority. Their leader was found and enlighted by a far-ancient presence, bestowed with infinite power. in a short time that Midworld was conquered by darkness and Whelingnorther Alliance began to spread their activities across the known universe.\n\nRecently they seem to be becoming active again and preparing to achieve their ultimate goal - the Whelingnorther Apocalypse.</description>
